Full Description: Blocvox is a community opinion platform that strengthens communities by making personal involvement easy, effective and fun. Ordinary people face incredible challenges in reaching large audiences online, regardless of how creative and useful their ideas are. At the same time, communities struggle to be heard by their official leaders, the media and the public. Blocvox solves this conundrum by connecting individuals and groups in a mutually beneficial way. At its core is a democratic discussion engine that empowers ordinary people to circumvent weak leaders and sensationalistic media, to foster authentic understanding between groups, and to move discussions beyond the echo chamber and into the public sphere.
